      "text": "## Overview"
    },
    {
      "id": 3,
      "tau": "instruction",
      "file": "SKILL.md",
      "parent": 2,
      "is_header": false,
      "text": "This skill guides agents in manipulating Excel (.xlsx) spreadsheets using Python."
    },
    {
      "id": 4,
      "tau": "instruction",
      "file": "SKILL.md",
      "parent": 2,
      "is_header": false,
      "text": "**Primary libraries**: `openpyxl` (structure-preserving read/write), `pandas` (data transformation). Never use any other"
    },
    {
      "id": 5,
      "tau": "section",
      "file": "SKILL.md",
      "parent": 1,
      "is_header": true,
      "text": "## Common Workflow"
    },
    {
      "id": 6,
      "tau": "instruction",
      "file": "SKILL.md",
      "parent": 5,
      "is_header": false,
      "text": "1. **Explore** the input file: run `python scripts/inspect.py` to list sheets,"
    },
    {
      "id": 7,
      "tau": "instruction",
      "file": "SKILL.md",
      "parent": 5,
      "is_header": false,
      "text": "inspect headers, and check dimensions."
    },
    {
      "id": 8,
      "tau": "instruction",
      "file": "SKILL.md",
      "parent": 5,
      "is_header": false,
      "text": "2. **Write `solution.py`** using `scripts/template.py` as the skeleton — it"
    },
    {
      "id": 9,
      "tau": "instruction",
      "file": "SKILL.md",
      "parent": 5,
      "is_header": false,
      "text": "defines `INPUT_PATH` and `OUTPUT_PATH` at the top."
    },
    {
      "id": 10,
      "tau": "instruction",
      "file": "SKILL.md",
      "parent": 5,
      "is_header": false,
      "text": "3. Choose the library according to the Library Selection table."
    },
    {
      "id": 11,
      "tau": "instruction",
      "file": "SKILL.md",
      "parent": 5,
      "is_header": false,
      "text": "4. **Execute** `python solution.py` and verify the output file was created."
    },
    {
      "id": 12,
      "tau": "instruction",
      "file": "SKILL.md",
      "parent": 5,
      "is_header": false,
      "text": "5. **Confirm** the target cells/range contain the expected values."
    },
    {
      "id": 13,
      "tau": "section",
      "file": "SKILL.md",
      "parent": 1,
      "is_header": true,
      "text": "## Library Selection"
